text = "Thank You:

Blaise Muller - Inventor of Quarto, 
whose mechanic was shamelessly stolen for this game.

Team Dogpit - Hosts of my favorite ongoing jam. 
This is not an appeal to the judges.

Godot Engine Developers - For this engine.
And for making an engine whose UI toolkit does not cause dispair.

And thank YOU for playing!"
